### 1. **The Logbook** *(Nautical Journal)*
A ship captain's log meets literary journal. Navy + brass palette, entries dated with faux coordinates, rope-style dividers, serif typography. Every post feels like a dispatch from sea. Unforgettable detail: coordinates under each post title, like *"45°N 9°E — Lake Como, June"*

